verdict.comment: Irish raider COCO LIGHTNING is 0-17 but she was a promising third on her recent stable debut and this could be a good opportunity.

comments.Be The Difference: Won here last month; tailed off here since but he's not written off
comments.Blame Rose: Two wins last spring; key player if at the top of her game on this first run since
comments.Call Him Now: Represents in-form yard but he was tailed off at Doncaster only last Friday
comments.Coco Lightning: 0-17 but good third on recent stable debut and this Irish raider is firmly in calculations
comments.Dorcas Road: Pulled up/soundly beaten on both starts for this yard and she's now 0-7
comments.Limerick Leader: Respectable fourth on both outings for this yard and he might not be far away
comments.Present Fair: Down to a handy mark but tailed off the last twice and needs to turn things around
comments.Quian: Below par on recent stable debut but a case can be made on his late 2024 form
comments.Reforme: Down the field at big odds in both handicaps and needs to leave those runs miles behind
